{"word":"G4682 - σπαράσσω - sparássō - spar-as'-so - Rend","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σπαράσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sparássō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">spar-as'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Rend</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அலைக்கழி"},{"paragraph":"to convulse"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Prolongation from <b>&#x03C3;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C9;</b> <b>spairo&#x0304;&#x0304;</b> (to <i>gasp</i>; apparently strengthened from <a href=\"#/G4685 - σπάω - spáō - spah'-o/4685\">G4685</a> through the idea of <i>spasmodic</i> contraction); to <i>mangle</i>, that is, <i>convulse</i> with epilepsy: - rend, tear.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}